-- BASF to Build New Water Treatment, Paper Chemicals Plant at Nanjing Site
-- B y   A n g e l a   C u l l e n
-- 2010-09-27T05:34:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-27/basf-to-build-new-water-treatment-paper-chemicals-plant-at-nanjing-site.html
BASF SE announced plans to build a
world-scale water treatment and paper chemicals plant at its
Nanjing site in China that will start production in the third
quarter of 2012, it said in a statement on its website today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  